Depends: bash (>= 4.0), fzf, mpv, jq, wlrmbg | xwallpaper | swaybg
Recommends: ffmpeg, libnotify-bin
Suggests: gtk-4-examples, python3-gi
Description: Video wallpaper manager for Hyprland/Wayland
 A sleek, feature-rich video wallpaper manager designed specifically for
 Hyprland and Wayland compositors.
 .
 Features include:
  * Interactive TUI picker using fzf
  * GTK4 GUI with thumbnails
  * Random, smart-random, and slideshow modes
  * Multi-monitor support with spanning
  * Favorites and history tracking
  * PyWal colorscheme integration
  * Time-based wallpaper switching
  * Desktop menu integration
